Here's a **full advanced structure** for a **Node.js + MongoDB** application that handles:  

âœ… **Wallet Recharge** (Add funds to the user wallet)  
âœ… **Subscription Purchase** (Deduct funds and activate subscription)  
âœ… **Transaction Table** (Track all wallet & subscription transactions)  
âœ… **Stripe Integration** (For real payments)  
âœ… **Common Payment Function** (Reusable for recharge & subscriptions)  

---

## **ðŸ“‚ Project Folder Structure**
```
/your_project
â”‚-- /config
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ db.js              # MongoDB Connection
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ stripe.js          # Stripe Configuration
â”‚-- /controllers
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ paymentController.js # Payment Logic
